text: Ishimovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baymurzinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 193 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 46 km from Mishkino, 8 km from Baymurzino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Ishimovo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
